## What the tests cover

| Category | Key concerns validated |
|---|---|
| **Search by Name** | Exact, partial, case-insensitive match; empty / whitespace input; cross-clinician isolation |
| **Search by MRN** | Exact match; uniqueness invariant; MRN belonging to another clinician returns nothing; invalid format |
| **Search by DOB** | Exact date match; shared DOB across clinicians; future date rejection; ISO string parsing |
| **Combined criteria** | Narrowing behaviour; conflicting criteria; missing all criteria |
| **Authorization** | Unauthenticated or inactive clinician raises error; no cross-panel leakage across multiple query types |
| **Result structure** | Correct Python type; required fields present; no duplicate records |
| **Edge cases** | SQL-injection-style input; oversized strings; downstream service failure; panel size ceiling |
